Gang of brolly-clad thieves targeted 13 shops in Tipton, West Midlands .
They stole £2,000 worth of cigarettes and cars valued at £30,000 .
Gang also threatened shop workers with hammers, knives and screwdrivers .
Police caught the thieves following a raid on an Asda supermarket in Coseley .
Men have been jailed for more than 27 years after pleading guilty to conspiracy to rob .